<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.9.10">
<l>vaṇṭaṟai poḻilti ruppēr variyara vaṇaiyil paḷḷi</l>
<l>koṇṭuṟai kiṉṟa mālaik koṭimatiḷ māṭa maṅkai</l>
<l>tiṇṭiṟal tōḷka liyaṉ ceñcolāl moḻinta mālai</l>
<l>koṇṭivai pāṭi yāṭak kūṭuvār nīḷvi cumpē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When they dance, singing these, having learned this garland [of verse]</l>
<l>Spoken with fine words by strong-armed, courageous Kaliyaṉ of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">its mansions with bannered walls,</l>
<l>About Māl who dwells, sleeping on a striped serpent couch, in Tiruppēr</l>
<l>With groves where bees hum, they will gather in the vast heavens.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
